  "video_id": "6N9BibH4g6g",
  "title": "A Narrated Reenactment of a Real-Life Story | \"God's True Love\" (English Dubbed)",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12100.0,
      "end_time": 17701.0,
      "text": "Accompanied by a cry that pierced the peace of the night sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17701.0,
      "end_time": 21000.0,
      "text": "I arrived in this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21000.0,
      "end_time": 28670.0,
      "text": "I had my family around me and a life that was my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 28670.0,
      "end_time": 33734.0,
      "text": "No one told me how all of this had come about."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 33734.0,
      "end_time": 40934.0,
      "text": "Everything just seemed to be as it should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 40934.0,
      "end_time": 42766.0,
      "text": "Slowly, I grew up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 42767.0,
      "end_time": 48701.0,
      "text": "and everything I came into contact with was fresh and new."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 48701.0,
      "end_time": 53767.0,
      "text": "I could do the things I liked to do and be with people I liked to be with."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 53767.0,
      "end_time": 56334.0,
      "text": "I was living in my own little world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 56334.0,
      "end_time": 61634.0,
      "text": "looking forward so hopefully to my future."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 61634.0,
      "end_time": 65801.0,
      "text": "Not realizing, I began striving for fame and fortune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 65801.0,
      "end_time": 70100.0,
      "text": "rushing around for future prospects and destiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 70100.0,
      "end_time": 72601.0,
      "text": "I believed that knowledge was power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 72601.0,
      "end_time": 76334.0,
      "text": "and that happiness came from human struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 76334.0,
      "end_time": 82667.0,
      "text": "I came to believe more and more in serving anyone who furthered my own interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 85670.0,
      "end_time": 91399.0,
      "text": "But every time I got back home, I felt like collapsing onto my bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 93367.0,
      "end_time": 95601.0,
      "text": "It was so exhausting!"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 97334.0,
      "end_time": 100634.0,
      "text": "Every day I had to live under a façade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 100634.0,
      "end_time": 103367.0,
      "text": "with nothing my heart could truly depend on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 103367.0,
      "end_time": 107400.0,
      "text": "nothing that could truly comfort it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 107400.0,
      "end_time": 113434.0,
      "text": "I would often stare blankly at the ceiling, silently asking myself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 113434.0,
      "end_time": 117366.0,
      "text": "Is this really how life should be lived?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 120801.0,
      "end_time": 125534.0,
      "text": "Believe in God and you shall have peace!"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 136234.0,
      "end_time": 140667.0,
      "text": "It was You who allowed me the fortune to hear Your voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 140667.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "and who saved me from the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 150000.0,
      "text": "You said to me: Child, come home!"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 150000.0,
      "end_time": 154901.0,
      "text": "From the moment I understood Your eager will to save man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 154901.0,
      "end_time": 157334.0,
      "text": "I made a promise:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 157334.0,
      "end_time": 161834.0,
      "text": "I will follow You all my life!"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 161834.0,
      "end_time": 165334.0,
      "text": "I began to perform duty in the church."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 167400.0,
      "end_time": 169267.0,
      "text": "And after a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 169267.0,
      "end_time": 172601.0,
      "text": "the duty I performed achieved good results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 172601.0,
      "end_time": 174834.0,
      "text": "I felt so pleased with myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 174834.0,
      "end_time": 178934.0,
      "text": "immersed in the joy of excelling above my peers."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 178934.0,
      "end_time": 184234.0,
      "text": "I became more enthusiastic in my duty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 184234.0,
      "end_time": 189801.0,
      "text": "believing myself the person most considerate to God&#39;s will."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 189801.0,
      "end_time": 192299.0,
      "text": "I never expected …"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 194534.0,
      "end_time": 197367.0,
      "text": "When you do things, you dislike discussing them with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 197367.0,
      "end_time": 199834.0,
      "text": "You do whatever you wish and can&#39;t coordinate with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 199834.0,
      "end_time": 202234.0,
      "text": "You argue right and wrong, true and false."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 202234.0,
      "end_time": 204801.0,
      "text": "You guard your position, not protecting the interests of God&#39;s family."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 204801.0,
      "end_time": 205367.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 205367.0,
      "end_time": 209566.0,
      "text": "In your work, you always preach letters and doctrines and talk down to people."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 209567.0,
      "end_time": 211534.0,
      "text": "You restrict all the brothers and sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 211534.0,
      "end_time": 214767.0,
      "text": "You should stop your duty and do spiritual self-examination!"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 214767.0,
      "end_time": 219000.0,
      "text": "Oh, no! It can&#39;t be! You must listen to me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 387934.0,
      "end_time": 392968.0,
      "text": "God&#39;s stern words, being pruned and dealt with by my brothers and sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 392968.0,
      "end_time": 395834.0,
      "text": "left me ashamed."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 395834.0,
      "end_time": 398567.0,
      "text": "I realized I had gone astray."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 398567.0,
      "end_time": 402234.0,
      "text": "God had not deemed me praiseworthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 402234.0,
      "end_time": 407267.0,
      "text": "I was at a loss, so much so that I began to doubt."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 407267.0,
      "end_time": 413400.0,
      "text": "Oh God! You brought me back home at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 413400.0,
      "end_time": 416200.0,
      "text": "You saved me."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 416200.0,
      "end_time": 418700.0,
      "text": "But why do You now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 421330.0,
      "end_time": 427334.0,
      "text": "Do You not love me, not want me anymore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 427334.0,
      "end_time": 435534.0,
      "text": "Am I thus exposed and abandoned by You?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 537762.0,
      "end_time": 539462.0,
      "text": "And so—"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 539457.0,
      "end_time": 542824.0,
      "text": "I still have hope of being saved?!"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 548601.0,
      "end_time": 558868.0,
      "text": "But I am so corrupted, so dirty— can I still hope to be saved?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 564367.0,
      "end_time": 571233.0,
      "text": "No. God just doesn&#39;t love me."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 571234.0,
      "end_time": 581234.0,
      "text": "These words are not meant for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 713701.0,
      "end_time": 717100.0,
      "text": "Yes! Oh God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 717100.0,
      "end_time": 719567.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not as I imagined You were."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 719567.0,
      "end_time": 724734.0,
      "text": "No matter what You do, it&#39;s all done to save us."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 724734.0,
      "end_time": 732534.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my fault for not knowing You, doubting You, misunderstanding You."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 732534.0,
      "end_time": 737670.0,
      "text": "Oh God! I wish to lay down all my burdens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 737670.0,
      "end_time": 742670.0,
      "text": "pursue the truth, and seek to know You!"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 744367.0,
      "end_time": 748666.0,
      "text": "And yet, the onset of a sudden serious illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 748667.0,
      "end_time": 753167.0,
      "text": "caused my heart to start complaining again."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 753167.0,
      "end_time": 760670.0,
      "text": "Oh God! Are You punishing me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 760670.0,
      "end_time": 765934.0,
      "text": "Please tell me what is Your will?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 867000.0,
      "end_time": 873767.0,
      "text": "At that moment, I was able to perceive Your good intentions."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 1192890.0,
      "end_time": 1199256.0,
      "text": "Amen! All the glory be to Almighty God!"
    }
  ]
}